data.description: This is absolutely one of Dayton's most incredible and unique homes. This majestic 4 bed, 3 ba Victorian exudes remarkable charm and the fascination of yesteryear. The home displays many of the original moldings, hardwood, and designs while being accompanied by some tasteful updates. Magnificent views of the foothills and Blues can be seen from the amazing semi rounded great room with virtually wall to wall windows. The home is located on Syndicate Hill with over a half acre lot that features beautiful trees, plantings, and tremendous patio with a rock fireplace, perfect for relaxing cozy outside evening or morning cup of coffee. Truly a diamond with a few rough edges just needing your TLC, dreams, and passion to be a finished stunning gem.
